<plot>Stationed in a Latin American country, sailor Stan is lonely and wants company. He tries to get his Chief to bring him along to a dinner the Chief has been invited to, but the Chief wants nothing to do with Stan. Nonetheless, Stan contrives to arrive at the dinner, where he becomes entranced with the young and pretty hostess -- much to the chagrin of the Chief and of her local swain, Vermicelli.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?391539</url></doc>
